<headline>Special Weather Statement issued April 06 at 8:39AM EDT  by NWS Albany</headline>
<description>...Areas of dense fog over the region this morning...
Areas of dense fog will affect the mid Hudson Valley, Litchfield
Hills and Berkshires through this morning. Visibilities will be a
half mile or less.
Motorists should drive with extra caution this morning as
visibilities may change rapidly. Slow down, leave extra distance
between vehicles, and use low beam headlights. Visibilities are
expected to quickly improve before noon.</description>
